<Document>
  <name>CalCOFI Current 113 Station Map</name>
  <description><![CDATA[113 CalCOFI Station Pattern;
Blue Markers = Standard 64 Station Pattern
Purple Markers = 3500m Basin stations
Red Markers = 9 SCCOOS Stations
Blue &amp; Blue-Green = Winter-Spring extended pattern ]]></description>
